## Replace these two values with your real project IDs before enabling the release workflow.
## CurseForge project ID: visible in the project URL on curseforge.com
## Wago project ID: visible in your project dashboard on addons.wago.io
curse-id: REPLACE_WITH_CURSEFORGE_PROJECT_ID
wago-project-id: REPLACE_WITH_WAGO_PROJECT_ID

## Libs are embedded in the repo — no externals needed.

enable-nolib-creation: no
